                		<h4><span>About the Author</span></h4>
                        
                        <div class="image"><img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/47c8faee740bed4bda1993ad967a1879?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/47c8faee740bed4bda1993ad967a1879?s=160&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-80 photo' height='80' width='80' /></div>
                        
                        <p>Helen is a journalist and dedicated Brixton resident who recently completed a Masters in African Politics at SOAS. She is Interested in politics and cycling, and comes from France and South Africa.</p>
                        
